features: Doody-catchers. Crap-sacks. Tinkle-poopers. Whatever you want to call them, our plant-based, super soft and absorbent disposable diapers are a modern convenience you don't want to live without
Say Hello to adorable Surprise designs. And say Goodbye to plain diapers. Our Surprise patterns are curated with girl and gender-neutral assortments for every parent's need. Go ahead, take your pick!
MADE WITHOUT: parabens, phthalates...basically, it's made with the good stuff.
Includes (1) 128ct surprise pack of diapers in girl & gender neutral designs for newborns and infants (Size NB)
Hello Bello believes in giving back and has donated over 7 million diapers (and a heckuva lot of wipes and care products) to parents in need
body.description: Hello Bello Premium Baby Diapers are designed by parents, so we know first-hand that preventing leaks and blowouts is a must. Been there, done that, don't want to deal with it. We also wanted to create a diaper with ingredients we could be proud of, that was soft on sensitive skin, and was made with just as much consideration for the planet we live on as the babies we love - all at an affordable price. So that's just what we did. Box contains 128 count size NB disposable baby diapers in Surprise Girl & Gender Neutral patterns.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Brand Promises Premium For All You shouldn’t have to choose between what’s best for your baby and what’s best for your budget. Our mission is to create the highest quality products at the most reasonable cost, because we believe every child deserves the best. Happier Babies, Happier Planet We love your littles, so from using organic botanicals in our body care to running our facilities on renewable energy, our products are thoughtfully created to be safe and effective for babies, and better for their world. Our Parent Pledge Parenting is hard for everyone, but much harder for those without adequate support. We’ve donated over 6 million diapers and are fighting for policy changes that will help end diaper need. We pledge to help however we can.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Happy Tushy, Happy Wallet :)
reviews.reviewText: These are pretty good diapers. They fit my baby just right, good quality, no leakage, great coverage, affordable, cute & environmentally friendly. These are a win!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars We’ve been happy with these!
reviews.reviewText: We’ve been pretty happy with these diapers! They are pretty absorbent, the fasteners are excellent and the design is pretty cute! I expected lower quality because of the price. I’m a happy customer!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Super stiff, not typical quality
reviews.reviewText: I’ve bought Hello Bello once before and they were great. They were soft, we didn’t have any leaks, and comparable to Kirkland’s or Huggies. The order I just received almost felt old… they were so stiff, thin, and leaked several times a day. Felt like a totally different brand! I’m scared to order again bc of the risk it may be like 2nd order I received.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: If you have a big newborn, with chunky thighs, these are for you. My baby is 9lb11oz and these are too big. She had leaks, and problems with the diaper not fitting snuggly around her thighs and bottom. They are soft and the prints are very cute, just very large to be considered newborn size.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 21, 2022
reviews.reviewText: The only downside to this brand is that I WISH they carried the newborn size in stores where I live. Other than that the price point is great and we know that little ones can go through diapers extremely fast. It has a good absorbency and a wet line indicator for new parents.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: First of all, I loved the print. But I did have a couple diaper’s separate from the printed plastic and cloth lining. I liked the wetness indicator but I wish it was clearer

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The diapers are pretty small and have little to no stretch. They’re not very absorbent so you have to try to change it as soon as it gets soiled. Also have had a lot more leaks with these because of that. Would not repurchase. Also nothing really girly about the “girl pattern” if anything it’s the opposite.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Kind of small
reviews.reviewText: Small in comparison to other diapers. Often had leaks overnight, but fine during the day. Cute print & soft. Just wish they came up a little higher in front/back
Adorable design, extremely soft but does not hold a lot of absorbency like the other brands. I went back to Huggies but Hello Bello is still worth a try!
